Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:27.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:31.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only seven of the eight are present.\NThat means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:34.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably killed one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:39.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To further the growth of\Nthe Yotsuba Group...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:42.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who should we kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:45.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:47.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.\NIf this keeps up...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:51.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that, we have several topics\Nwhich we should discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is Hatori's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:56.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:00.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,\NI'm relieved that he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira has clearly shown\Nwhat'll happen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.80,0:02:07.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to whoever tries\Nto leave these meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:08.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.97,0:02:12.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we all know what\NHatori's death means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:14.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.64,0:02:18.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Eraldo Coil's report...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.98,0:02:23.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of their partners just died.\NIs that it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.86,0:02:28.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Five million dollars.\NJust for this report, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't found anything\Nimportant about L,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:35.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like his face and name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:39.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Coil really of any use?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:40.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:43.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of this report...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:48.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Coil warns us that we shouldn't\Ntake L's existence lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:51.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It says, "lf you continue with your\Ncurrent pace of killing..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:55.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"for Yotsuba's benefit...\Nevery week on Fridays and Saturdays..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:59.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"L could possibly connect\Nyou with Kira."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:07.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impressive that Coil has\Nfigured out what we've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we should stop killing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:12.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,every weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:16.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing.\NIt's like they're confessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:18.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we have this video,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:21.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we could probably arrest\Nall seven of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:27.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira isn't very flexible either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.88,0:03:30.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice if he killed\Nat various times during the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.47,0:03:33.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Coil noticed this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:36.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,makes it dangerous to\Ncontinue killing at our current pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on,\Nwe should be even more careful
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:42.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and make sure nobody ever notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, on to the main topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:48.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who shall we kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.74,0:03:54.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We must stop E.L.F. Insurance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,from expanding their business\Ninto the Japan market.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:04:00.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yotsuba and many other companies'\Nclients will be swept away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:01.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:06.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is it all right for these people\Nfrom E.L.F. to die by accidental deaths?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.51,0:04:09.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they do this so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:16.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another person is Santaro Zenzai,\Na member of the Kugisawa Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:19.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's protesting Yotsuba's plans\Nfor the resort development.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:22.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Zenzai suffers from\Nhigh blood pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:26.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...it is possible to have him\Ndie of a stroke at a designated time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:27.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:28.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:32.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira...death by accident...\Ndeath by disease...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,designated time of deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:38.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as we thought.\NThere's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:44.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Unfortunately, we can only say that\Nafter those people they named die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:51.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we continue to monitor\Nwhat these seven say at their meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:57.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,their actions, and whether\Nthe people they name die...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll definitely catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:01.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.02,0:05:05.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NBoth of you in unison...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go along with your idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:09.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:11.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to plan on catching Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:17.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by allowing these seven to\Ncontinue to kill, but I can't let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:21.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's apparent that\Nthese seven are committing murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:26.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we prove it's them by\NMatsuda's testimony and this footage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.09,0:05:29.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we caught them now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:33.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,everything we've done until\Nnow will go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the E.L.F. will be three weeks later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:41.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ask Kira to have Zenzai\Nkilled this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:41.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:46.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's this weekend,\Nthere's not much time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:50.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you know the cell phone numbers\Nof those seven, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:51.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Any one of them will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to call one of those seven\Nand stop the killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:57.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:02.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we do that just three days\Nafter Aiber's made contact with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll arouse suspicion that\Nour investigation is catching up to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:08.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's also highly unlikely
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:12.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that we won't be able to\Nfigure out who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We came this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:16.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but we'll have to start back\Nat the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to catch Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:25.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we need proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:30.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is among these seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't it fair to assume that\Nif we call one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a one in seven chance that\Nthat person is Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:42.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At most, I would think there's\Ntwo of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's two out of seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're prepared to let them know
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that the investigation is\Ncatching up to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then let's risk it on those odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to borrow\Nthe name "L", Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:55.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From the sound of the conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:57.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who seems the least\Nlikely to be Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:07:00.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and who carries some\Nweight on the board is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Ooi!\N- Namikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:06.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to make a call,\Nuse this phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:09.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be traced or tapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really think it would\Nbe faster if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we killed the executives of\Nour rival companies one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be going a bit far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kill them and\Nsplit their stocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.78,0:07:23.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Reiji Namikawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the V.P. of Yotsuba Group's\NSales Department One, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:28.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:31.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen and respond as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:33.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am L.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:41.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have cameras and wiretaps\Nplanted in that meeting room...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:43.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm recording footage\Nof your entire meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:46.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The opening topic was Hatori's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.64,0:07:49.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're debating who to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:51.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:53.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been watching everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:55.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:59.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or if you aren't someone who\Ncan directly contact Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then let's make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:08.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delay the death of E.L.F.'s president\Nand Mr. Zenzai one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:11.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This shouldn't be difficult for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes, I see...\N- If we want to randomize the deaths...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:16.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Yes... Go on...\N- we should just throw darts at a calendar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:22.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and cooperate with us from now on,\Nyour crime...no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:25.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone other than\NKira will not be charged...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,under the belief that they were\Nthreatened by Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,into participating in the meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:31.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:33.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My only option is join L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:37.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be killed if Kira finds out\Nthat I've sided with L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:38.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:41.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you reveal this conversation,\Nit'll cause a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:44.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There would be no advantage for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:50.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But my goal is to go\None on one against Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:54.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen... If L wins against Kira,\Nyou'll be acquitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:58.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira wins against me,\Nyou'll carry on with your luxurious life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:03.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or you can remain a spectator and\Ngo along with either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:08.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever wins, L or Kira,\Nit's no loss to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:12.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it would be a loss\Nto you if you were caught right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already knows the answer\NI would have given.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:19.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. On Monday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:25.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Namikawa?\NWho was it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, a subordinate of mine\Nmessed up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll have to fix it on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:33.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for interrupting.\NLet's get back on topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:37.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding when we should kill\Nthose E.L.F. guys and Zenzai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we give Coil one month\Nto discover L's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:49.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't, we'll be forced to\Nkill them at various dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:53.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we'll give him another month\Nand repeat the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've dealt with L,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll go back to two to\Nthree people a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:10:01.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we should make\Ndealing with L our first priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:03.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:07.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. If we kill L,\Nwe won't have anything in our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, we should be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... It sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:15.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we've got to be\Nextremely careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:18.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll give Coil one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:20.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No objections.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L...you're probably satisfied with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll still hold these meetings\Nevery week.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:27.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:29.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It went well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:30.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:33.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:35.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did you delay the killing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:39.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we may be able to get\Ninformation from Namikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:42.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it looked like\Nsomething I would do...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:45.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought of it faster than I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:47.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:54.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if I die, it's quite possible you would be\Ncapable of succeeding the title of L.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking about\Nsuch morbid things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:00.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a month to figure out\NKira's identity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:02.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and gather evidence against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The challenge is just beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:05.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:09.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one who\Nfirst noticed Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be more capable than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:16.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.64,0:11:19.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would you take over for me as L?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, would you take over for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:44.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As L.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:49.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is all an act and he is Kira,\Nhe's sure to say yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:56.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we have this,\Nwon't we die together?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:11:59.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:01.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:05.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm going to tell everyone\Nwhat you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:09.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki thinks that if I'm Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:14.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,either I'm just pretending I'm not him\Nand putting on an act...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:17.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or Kira's power has passed\Nto someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I have no memory\Nthat I was Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two possibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.71,0:12:24.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the first...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:28.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm putting on an act,\Nthese handcuffs will never come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, even if it was\Nthe other possibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:33.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he probably wouldn't take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.43,0:12:36.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki thinks that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:39.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that power has been\Npassed to someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:42.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he assumes that I would have\Nplanned things
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:44.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to have it return to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:48.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, he doesn't think\NI was being controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed the power on
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:54.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and planned for it to come back\Nto me once I've been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:59.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...You figured out exactly\Nwhat I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki's line of reasoning is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:05.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Light will become Kira\Nonce he steals L's position."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:07.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To acquire the position of L...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and be able to freely control\Nthe police,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,while being Kira in secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would be the ultimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:20.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could do that...no, I would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you meant, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:24.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:25.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:30.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know by now that\NI'm probably not acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:35.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were acting and\Ntrying to steal my position...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way that you'd reveal\Nyour plan in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:42.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:50.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after I catch the current Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:51.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,do you really think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'd become Kira, a murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like that kind of person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:04.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so. You look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:14.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Once is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.91,0:14:19.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave it as a draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:21.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:25.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we have\Nto catch the Kira before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:28.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have the handcuffs,\Nyou shouldn't have any complaints.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:32.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.\NWe only have a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:34.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:35.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:40.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can use that meeting\Nas evidence against those seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,won't the murders of criminals stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:43.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:45.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:47.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:50.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not sure if Kira\Nis among those seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:55.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they just have a connection to him,\NKira will simply kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:59.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to be absolutely sure\Nthat Kira is among them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,or there's no point in\Ncatching them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's difficult to determine\Nwho's Kira right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's still too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:14.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you can't say that\Nhe's definitely among the seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:18.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there's still a chance that the killings\Nwill stop if we arrest them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:22.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like my dad says.\NThere is a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:23.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, on second thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:27.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll go after Kira by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:33.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use these headquarters,\Nas will l.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:38.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do things your way\Nand arrest them if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:41.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall investigate as\NI wish in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll only get into arguments\Nif we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split and act separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:50.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you just want to\Nfigure out who Kira is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.25,0:15:55.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This case will never be\Nsolved if we don't capture him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.84,0:15:58.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say that stopping\Nthe deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.17,0:16:00.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of people before us is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:04.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't find the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:07.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will appear again and\Nthe victims will increase in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:12.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... I think it's more important\Nto figure out who Kira is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:17.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm opposed to arresting those seven,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:20.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if you want to do that,\Nthen you take responsibility for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:23.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pursue Kira by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We only have one month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who will be faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:30.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:31.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amane's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:35.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Light, I know you're\Non your father's side, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remove these handcuffs,\Nso you're going to have to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light! Was today a day\Nwe could go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:52.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Mr. Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:54.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you love Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you also worship Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:04.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:05.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:08.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would you pick, Light or Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:08.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.50,0:17:11.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:14.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful to Kira and\Nwanted to meet him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:17.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but that's not love. Definitely Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light wants to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to catch him.\NNow what'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:31.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Light wants to catch him,\Nthen I want Light to catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:35.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So would you want to help\NLight by working with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on the investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:41.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll do anything for Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:44.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second.\NWhat are you thinking of doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:48.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiber will pose as Eraldo Coil\Nand tell those seven that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:52.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he learned that Misa Amane might\Nbe able to identify L.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:55.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that L brought her in\Nfor questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because he suspected that\Nshe was the Second Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:17:59.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:03.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If they know that Misa Amane\Nmight know L...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:07.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll have her appear in\Ntheir commercials
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:10.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and try to ask her about\Nvarious things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Mr. Matsuda's screw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:15.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there were talks about using her\Nin their commercials.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:18.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:19.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it would subject\Nyou to danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You're worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:26.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:31.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is nothing if it's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.45,0:18:35.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Misa, if they know that\Nyou might know who L is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we don't know what means they'll use\Nto get that information out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:43.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I won't say anything\Nunder any kind of torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:48.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Kira can control\Nhis victims' actions before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:49.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a good chance that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:52.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he might try to get her\Nto talk and kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:55.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if he kills L, then he won't have\Nany use for her and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:57.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira would kill Misa to keep her silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:00.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:04.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we win, Misa won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.65,0:19:06.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:09.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as long as we're handcuffed,\Nwe'll share the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, you'll die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:16.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Misa is the one\Nwho would grieve the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:21.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's either we both die,\Nor we catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:22.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now which will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:26.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch Kira!\NI can't live in a world without Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:27.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuzaki, that's messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:32.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no time.\NI'm desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:37.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Misa Amane's...\Nbravery and love for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:38.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,have no equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.65,0:19:41.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:45.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've misunderstood\Nyou all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.36,0:19:47.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I called you a pervert and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:51.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do understand me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:56.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Misa is the perfect,\Nmost worthy woman for Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:57.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:19:59.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:02.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could fall in love with you,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:04.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... That's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.71,0:20:07.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How about being friends, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:08.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.38,0:20:11.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made another friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:15.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. All of Light's friends are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:25.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't ever betray\Nany of my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.61,0:20:27.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With our powers combined,\Nlet's arrest Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami is taking a different investigative\Napproach from us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:34.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and working with\Nhis father and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I will be together, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dirty, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:43.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now my only choice is to\Njoin your investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:44.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NLight will be joining us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:49.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:53.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm opposed to this investigation.\NIt's too dangerous for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:54.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:57.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for thinking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:21:01.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But let me do this.\NI want to be of use to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.02,0:21:04.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be of use to you and\NI want you to love me even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:06.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides that, l...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:09.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,would gladly die for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:13.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Arresting seven people in\Nthis situation is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi, Matsuda,\Ndo you have any good ideas?
