Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:41.60,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A fleeting tactic in the eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:46.19,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Without petition evil against the law\Nchain it in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.77,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Poison the notebook fear the lust
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:51.65,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Delusion of being deceived\Nperpetually drooling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.28,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Judgement is "crime control" they driveled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.95,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Who has the Rx for that?
