Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:02.62,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A sanctioned word
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.87,0:22:06.42,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Taking in heat\NJust like "Pirates of Death"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:09.96,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Atone with the game of laws\NBilly in despair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:12.80,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Now, it's time for ethics\NNow, the unstoppable Eraser Rain
