Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:21.35,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The unstoppable Eraser Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.86,0:22:37.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:39.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Nishinaka, Light, the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:42.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And now even the Shinigami's\Nasking me to act!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:44.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:47.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I might be in a big commercial.\NI am so popular!
